Smackdown is here on tape delay from Glasgow, Scotland

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/e3683c71-6041-40f4-8ffa-1944c76a6e85/Screenshot_20240614_170552.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_NAOMI DEF. CHELSEA GREEN_**
    

Chelsea’s theme song now has Samantha Irvins introduction built in. Naomi picks up the win and they mock Chelsea and Piper as they make their way up the ramp

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/915bd952-351d-463a-a3b1-d248358ed2bf/Screenshot_20240614_171751.jpg?format=original)

Baron Corbin is in the GM office being greatful for getting called up. Legado De Fantasma walk in and call Corbin a charity case.

Santos Escobar tells Nick Aldis he heard Appolo is good to go so he wants a match.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/0341d8f8-d087-49e8-b057-3b8f853fac6f/Screenshot_20240614_172605.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_GRAYSON WALLER EFFECT FT. #DIY_**
    

DIY is not here to play around. They start throwing furniture and they tell Grayson Waller he’s trying to screw Austin Theory.

A brawl breaks out, Waller ducks a Johnny Gargano super kick and allows Austin Theory to take it. Gargano wasn’t trying to take out his former “the WAY” stablemate but there’s no time for concern as they clesr the ring and pose with the WWE Tag Team Championships.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/541e567f-8854-4725-b524-501fa8058829/Screenshot_20240614_173115.jpg?format=original)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/6f7a8521-25cb-41dd-9c21-795aedb8ee45/Screenshot_20240614_173850.jpg?format=original)

Blair Davenport mocks Naomi for winning her match while Bayley was at her side. Naomi is gonna attack her but Bayley says it isn’t worth it.

Bayley thanks Naomi for being by her aide even though it’s hard. They hug. Then they get distracted by Chelsea Green and attacked by Piper Niven

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/29b46701-cdb5-4322-b5be-726780758190/Screenshot_20240614_173938.jpg?format=original)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/48ca8a51-b3cb-4508-bf78-675b5b390595/Screenshot_20240614_174251.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_SANTOS ESCOBAR DEF. APOLLO CREWS_**
    

Crews is outnumbered until Baron Corbin comes out to even the odds. It looks like Crews is going to get a distraction victory but Santos kicks out.

Santos pulls out the win.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/338b2df9-b04d-4dfe-9b13-0b55d6608b40/FB_IMG_1718400581215.jpg?format=original)

“When it got tough, what’d you do Cody? You quit WWE. He also quit New Japan Pro Wrestling. You quit Ring of Honor. This man right here helped start up a company \[AEW\]…and you quit it too.”

— AJ Styles to Cody Rhodes

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/8c0ef211-507e-4ca0-86f3-aa91c0db86b1/20240614_183522.jpg?format=original)

LA Knight invades Logan Paul's house in Puerto Rico!

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/4db24260-d5c4-4951-a673-fc8320061554/Screenshot_20240614_182824.jpg?format=original)

The Bloodline is banned from ringside for taking out the Street Profits earlier tonight.

Solo tells Paul Heyman, if he loses to Kevin Owens tonight. Solo is going to take it out on Paul Heyman.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/e31b93a6-af3f-470f-b36d-09969eee461e/Screenshot_20240614_183404.jpg?format=original)

Alba Fyre and Isla Dawn cut a short genericpromo about their triple threat tag match at Clash at the Castle.

