*   ## **_SOLO SIKOA DEF. KEVIN OWENS_**
    

Randy Orton returns to save Kevin Owens from a Bloodline beatdown after Solo pins Kevin Owens in the main event of Smackdown

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/6056afb7-7641-4cc0-bad8-1a181b1cf020/Screenshot_20240614_185612.jpg?format=original)